N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 78.5 - Compliance with official directions required

State Regulations

No person shall use or otherwise conduct himself upon any
portion of the airport in a manner contrary to the posted or otherwise visually
indicated official directions applicable to that area. Notes
